ions about a specific industry that they believe may be temporaryguild provides active portfolio management the firm does not believe that portfolios must be fully invested in stocks at all times they look for opportunities with favorable rewardrisk parameters the firm employs an opportunistic style that is responsive to changes in the markets guild continuously reevaluates the asset allocations and positions in their portfolios when opportunities arise guild utilizes foreign currencies and foreign currency denominated cash equivalents to earn income and to capture appreciation from foreign exchange trends the firm also looks for investments that offer the potential to appreciate  in  months and that have a perceived rewardrisk potential of  to  website httpwwwguildinvestmentcom in the news see more relsci june   ari cohn is no longer serving in their position at guild investment management inc globenewswire november   equitiescom and guild investment management launch guilds market commentary on equitiespremiumcom see full news coverage and complete stories with relsci professional create your news feed see more executives  employees monty guild founder  cio anthony rutherford danaher president  portfolio manager aubrey ford director of client relations tim shirata executive vice president  business development ari cohn vice presidentinvestment operations rudi von abele senior research analyst bronwyn von abele marketing associate bronwyn guild administrative professional barbara reams administrative professional see our list of current and previous employees when you upgrade start my free trial ➤ see more paths to guild investment management inc guild investment management inc you connections via relationship science guild investment management inc sync your contacts to see how you can connect with guild investment management inc start my free trial ➤ see more holdings  top positions restricted data only for relsci professional users start my free trial ➤ see more